comments: Allen (BKN) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Curry (POR) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Nurkic (POR) legally contests Harris' (BKN) driving shot attempt.
Nurkic (POR) makes marginal body contact with Allen (BKN) in the lane that does not affect his ability to defend the pass or shot.
Allen (BKN) makes contact with Nurkic's (POR) wrist after the release of his shot attempt near the rim and does not affect his ability to follow through naturally.
Curry (POR) briefly grasps Harris' (BKN) jersey, but releases without affecting his FOM.
Curry (POR) has his hand rested on Russell's (BKN) side during the drive and maintains it there at the start of his upward shooting motion, but quickly retreats it without applying any force.
Allen (BKN) initiates body contact with Lillard (POR) that affects his SQBR.
Allen (BKN) establishes his screening position in the path of Harkless (POR) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
RLS shows Nurkic (POR) makes marginal contact with Dinwiddie's (BKN) off-arm after his gather.
LLS shows Harkless (POR) makes marginal contact with Allen's (BKN) right arm that does not impede his ability to retrieve the rebound.
Harkless (POR) makes contact with Allen's (BKN) right arm during his upward shooting motion and affects his shot attempt near the rim.
Harkless (POR) continues moving into Russell's (BKN) path after initial contact takes place during the pick, but the ensuing contact is marginal and does not affect Russell's ability to defend.
Nurkic (POR) and Dudley (BKN) engage and separate as the shot is released, and do not affect the other's ability to fight for the rebound.

RAR shows Lillard (POR) makes contact with Harris' (BKN) left arm, but it is marginal and does not affect his ability to maintain control of the ball after he secures the rebound. Harkless (POR) simultaneously makes contact with Harris' midsection, but also does not affect his ability to maintain control of the ball.
Nurkic (POR) makes marginal contact with Harris (BKN) that does not affect his ability to control the rebound.
RLS and MOB show Nurkic (POR) cleanly strips Harris (BKN) of the ball before making incidental contact to his knee.
Dudley (BKN) establishes legal guarding position outside of the RA and makes marginal body contact with Nurkic (POR) after the release of his shot attempt.
LLB shows Harkless (POR) makes marginal contact with Allen's (BKN) right arm that does not affect his ability to tap the ball to an opponent.
Curry (POR) makes contact across Russell's (BKN) arm after he secures the rebound.
Dinwiddie (BKN) extends his hand to the front of Lillard (POR) at the start of his drive but he is able to continue though the contact on his path to the basket.
Dinwiddie (BKN) makes marginal contact to the body of Lillard (POR) during his shooting motion that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Curry (POR) and Harris (BKN) engage and disengage without affecting the other's FOM.
Curry (POR) makes clean contact with the ball after Russell (BKN) loses control of it at the top of the perimeter.
LLB shows Russell (BKN) makes contact with Curry's (POR) left arm/shoulder, but it is marginal and does not affect his ability to gain control of the loose ball.
Dinwiddie (BKN) makes contact with his left arm across Curry's (POR) front and affects his SQBR.
[Observable in enhanced video] LAR shows Russell (BKN) slides his pivot foot after receiving the pass.
Harris (BKN) firms up in his screening position in Harkless' (POR) path and absorbs the contact as it is made during the pick.
Curry (POR) and Harkless (POR) legally contest Russell's (BKN) jump shot attempt.
Nurkic (POR) establishes a legal picking position by firming up and not delivering contact to Russell (BKN).
Dudley (BKN) gets his feet down and establishes a legal picking position absorbing the contact from Hood (POR).
Hood (POR) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Dinwiddie (BKN).
Nurkic (POR) and Dinwiddie (BKN) briefly engage during the pick, but then immediately disengage sliding each others arms off of one another.
Nurkic (PR) establishes a legal picking position and does not deliver contact to Dinwiddie (BKN).
Dudley (BKN) legally contests Nurkic's (POR) shot attempt near the rim as he firms up and absorbs the contact from Nurkic.
Nurkic (POR) and Dudley (BKN) briefly engage and disengage during the rebound attempt.
Carroll (BKN) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Harris (BKN) makes contact to the body of Curry (POR) during his shooting motion that affects his driving shot attempt.
Russell (BKN) maintains a legal pivot foot.
Nurkic (POR) makes marginal contact with Russell (BKN) during the driving shot attempt, and as Nurkic swipes down to attempt to block Russell's shot, he does not make contact with Russell's arm.
Nurkic (POR) establishes a legal picking position and absorbs the contact from Dinwiddie (BKN).
Dinwiddie (BKN) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Lillard (POR).
Carroll (BKN) clamps Nurkic's (POR) arm affecting his ability to retrieve the rebound.
RAR shows Dinwiddie (BKN) does not gather the ball with two hands after his dribble not committing a double dribble violation.
Hood (POR) maintains legal guarding position when he contests Dinwiddie's (BKN) driving shot attempt.
Curry (POR) and Harris (BKN) briefly engage and disengage during the rebound attempt.
Dinwiddie (BKN) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Lillard (POR).
Carroll (BKN) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Curry (POR).

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Russell (BKN) throws the ball out of bounds.
Harkless (POR) does not establish a legal picking position as he continues to take steps up the floor delivering contact to Dinwiddie (BKN), affecting his ability to get around the pick.
Harkless (POR) establishes a legal picking position and does not deliver contact to Dinwiddie (BKN).
Dudley (BKN) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Hood (POR).
Curry (POR) briefly engages with Dudley (BKN) as Dudley is cutting to the basket but disengages.
Curry (POR) maintains a legal guarding position during the play at the basket by Dudley (BKN).
Carroll (BKN) commits a take foul on Curry (POR).
Curry (POR) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Carroll (BKN).
Carroll (BKN) engages with Curry (POR) but does not affect his FOM during the inbound.
Dinwiddie (BKN) maintains a legal guarding position during the play at the basket by Harkless (POR).
Lillard (POR) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Harris (BKN).
Curry (POR) slightly extends his arm into Carroll (BKN) during the inbound but does not dislodge him from legal guarding position.  Carroll's reaction is not consistent with the level of contact.
Dinwiddie (BKN) commits a take foul on Hood (POR).
As Curry (POR) attempts to swipe down and make contact with the ball, he makes marginal contact with Dinwiddie's (BKN) leg, who is able to maintain possession of the ball and continue his drive.
Curry (POR) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Dinwiddie (BKN).
Harkless (POR) briefly places his hand to Russell's (BKN) front as the two are attempting to get over the screen, but Harkless disengages without affecting his FOM.
Dinwiddie (BKN) commits a take foul on Aminu (POR).
Lillard (POR) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Russell (BKN).
Aminu (POR) makes contact to the arm of Harris (BKN) during his shooting motion that affects his play at the basket.
Dudley (BKN) makes marginal contact to the body of Hood (POR) during his shooting motion as he cleanly blocks the ball.
LeVert (BKN) makes contact to the body of Lillard (POR) during his shooting motion that affects his play at the basket.
Hood (POR) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Harris (BKN).
